{"type": "article", "id": 12208, "title": "去麦当劳，吃顿“高级正餐”？", "description": "啊，快餐巨头们难以按捺的“正餐梦”！", "date": "2015-07-16T15:41:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13024, "name": "高级料理"}, {"id": 738, "name": "麦当劳"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702124608Eil1Bnm7spfuXKLN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span></span><span>不是逗你，这真的是麦当劳日本推出的“正餐”服务。</span><span>哦，做正餐的时候他们管自己叫作</span> “<span>Restaurant M”</span><span>。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124606phzwAfgGDkIQ16ve.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"359\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124606YWU2oOrDCpeZRbsF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"359\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124607E0Mk62mJLZOV4vPw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这项服务仅限 </span><span>7 </span><span>月 </span><span>27 </span><span>日一天，在晚餐时段限量招待 </span><span>20 </span><span>名客人，免费享用高级正餐形式的麦当劳食物，今天</span><span>(7 </span><span>月 </span><span>16 </span><span>日</span><span>)</span><span>起在日本官网接受报名。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124607Bl1VR7pwvZFxczsI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>麦当劳此举是为了推广其最新菜品“新鲜麦当劳”，该系列以蔬菜为主打食材，比如在汉堡里面加入西红柿和红辣椒。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140018hZE2j75HagwTI8WR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>麦当劳希望能用“五种馅料的西班牙竹签小吃</span><span>(pinchos)</span><span>”之类的呈现方式让消费者感受到麦当劳食材的高品质，以此弥补因食品卫生问题而受损的品牌形象。</span><span>   <br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124607p3HXdnMVmPB4Kusf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"400\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>《<em>王牌特工》剧照</em></span><em>  </em></span><br>\r\n<span></span><span> </span><span>实际上，关于麦当劳“高级料理”的调侃从没停止过。大反派瓦伦丁用一支</span><span> 1945</span><span> 年的拉菲搭配巨无霸汉堡，是前段时间大热的《王牌特工》中经典镜头之一。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140018GqVg7IKQew5yrOM6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"391\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/3049.html\" target=\"_blank\">我们此前也曾报道过</a>，外国网友将麦当劳重新装盘后，拿到美食展台谎称这是有机食品，请一群所谓的专家试吃。</span><span></span><span>没想到这些专家品尝后赞不绝口，还有人说“这当然比麦当劳好吃，因为是有机的嘛！”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>作为根本就是“消灭厨师”（一切都是标准化配料）的快餐巨头，肯德基此前也曾请来“名厨”刘一帆为产品代言。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140019Z1iXy4FE9NHQ52Lh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"403\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>刘一帆因为参与录制东方卫视《顶级厨师》节目而为观众所熟悉。<span>这位节目中严苛的“地狱厨师”在广告中对手撕猪肉堡欲罢不能的样子也是让人惊呆了。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>啊，梦想还是要有的，别太当真就好。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}